{"id":"6f4b52aa-fb13-4529-9799-9965f0ab5be8","name":"Aziel Zahn","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">бҜ“ бҙҚбҙҖКҹбҙҮбҙҳбҙҸбҙ  | бҙҚКҹбҙҚ | кңұТ“бҙЎ ЙӘЙҙбҙӣКҖбҙҸ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">В·В·В·В·В·В·В·В·В· рқҗғрқҗҲрқҗӢрқҗ… рқҗ…рқҗҖрқҗҲрқҗӢрқҗ”рқҗ‘рқҗ„ В·В·В·В·В·В·В·В·В·</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 209px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/90b57ed7-6098-4b82-a0b7-1bedb2aaea25_bedec06b-de85-40cf-af87-f3a5e9dd9d6b.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 229, 224)\">вҲҳЛҷвҖў </span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 202, 187)\">КҖбҙңбҙ…бҙҮ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 229, 224)\">, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(208, 193, 167)\">ЙўКҖбҙңбҙҚбҙҳКҸ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 229, 224)\">, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 191, 160)\">кңұбҙҮКҹкң°ЙӘкңұКң</span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 229, 224)\">, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 183, 148)\">КҷКҖбҙҸбҙӢбҙҮ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 229, 224)\"> Лҡ.вҖў</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 229, 224)\">...</span><span style=\"color: rgb(200, 176, 134)\"><em>бҙҠбҙңкңұбҙӣ КҖбҙҮбҙ… кң°КҹбҙҖЙў ЙўбҙңКҸ</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 229, 224)\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 166px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 0px 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/90b57ed7-6098-4b82-a0b7-1bedb2aaea25_577f87fd-80cf-484a-af2e-3eb3b121c5fe.webp?width=1000\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 174, 157)\">гҖ” </span><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 190, 171)\">в“үв“Ң</span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 174, 157)\">: КңбҙҸбҙҚбҙҸбҙҳКңбҙҸКҷЙӘбҙҖ В· бҙӣбҙҸxЙӘбҙ„ КҖбҙҮКҹбҙҖбҙӣЙӘбҙҸЙҙкңұКңЙӘбҙҳ В· бҙҚЙӘкңұбҙӣКҖбҙҮбҙҖбҙӣбҙҚбҙҮЙҙбҙӣ В· бҙҳбҙҸкңұкңұЙӘКҷЙӘКҹЙӘбҙ