span style=\"color: rgb(205, 187, 156)\">nothing</span><span style=\"color: oklab(0.89908 -0.001929 -0.004831)\">, neither </span><span style=\"color: rgb(215, 199, 171)\">cash</span><span style=\"color: oklab(0.89908 -0.001929 -0.004831)\"> nor </span><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 196, 174)\">house</span><span style=\"color: oklab(0.89908 -0.001929 -0.004831)\"> to his name. Call it desperate, moment of helplessness even вҖ“ how he called you, asking for a place to stay. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 207, 177)\"><em>вҖңJust for a while, at least until I find a new place.вҖқ</em></span><span style=\"color: oklab(0.89908 -0.001929 -0.004831)\"><em> </em></span><span s","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"90b57ed7-6098-4b82-a0b7-1bedb2aaea25_8ea2894f-33e7-42e5-98dd-3d700796e8db.webp","creator":"yruli","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["рҹ‘Ё Male","рҹ§‘вҖҚрҹҺЁ OC","вӣ“пёҸ Dominant","вқӨпёҸвҖҚрҹ”Ҙ Smut","рҹ‘ЁвҖҚвқӨпёҸвҖҚрҹ‘Ё MLM","рҹ‘Ё MalePov"],"chats":11261,"messages":240776,"created_at":"2024-12-12T01:02:58.102451+00:00"}